# Day 9 – NutriScope: AI-Powered Nutrition Dashboard

## Overview

Built **NutriScope**, a complete single-file HTML nutrition tracking application and then enhanced it through iterative AI-assisted development.

The project demonstrates how an MVP can be expanded into a more feature-rich application using structured prompts.

---

## Objective

- Build an MVP version of NutriScope.
- Enhance the application with additional functionality.
- Compare both versions.
- Understand iterative product development using AI.

---

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- Chart.js
- Claude AI

---

