# Enhanced Version Features

## Added Functionality

### CSV Upload Support

Users can upload food data through CSV files.

### Expanded Food Database

Added 40 additional food items for improved coverage.

### Additional Micronutrients

Expanded nutrient tracking beyond the MVP.

### 2-Day Meal Planner

Provides sample meal plans for two days.

### Risk Analysis

Identifies potential nutrient deficiencies and excesses.

### Educational Disclaimer

Provides informational guidance and responsible usage notice.

### Nutrition Sources

Displays nutritional information references.

### Improved Charts

Enhanced visual analytics and dashboard experience.

### Advanced Recommendations

Smarter suggestions based on dietary preference and nutrient status.

